    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a <strong>hand-drawn graphic adventure</strong> full of humor and investigation. A classic <strong>point-and-click</strong> experience packed with laughs, mysteries, and wildly quirky characters!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras/bb5edb09c477e26eefb0777d121714fc.poster.avif?t=1764149792\" width=800 height=322 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras/bb5edb09c477e26eefb0777d121714fc.webm?t=1764149792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras/bb5edb09c477e26eefb0777d121714fc.mp4?t=1764149792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Story</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tango Rio hasn’t seen his father in two years—not since he left with his uncle on “a journey that would change the world.” Or so he claimed. Then, silence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The only clue: the name of a Polynesian archipelago... and the feeling that this time, the escape is different.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What awaits him? <strong>Tropical legends, strange rituals, time travel, dark prophecies,</strong> and a bunch of totally crazy characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras/8441fec47ee7ad71e7961ddc183b71fc.poster.avif?t=1764149792\" width=800 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras/8441fec47ee7ad71e7961ddc183b71fc.webm?t=1764149792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras/8441fec47ee7ad71e7961ddc183b71fc.mp4?t=1764149792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Caught between wild puzzles and even wilder situations, Tango is about to dive into an adventure way beyond anything he ever expected.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras/aaede2db898b8752c0578f3d2cfd2ece.avif?t=1764149792\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras_big/aaede2db898b8752c0578f3d2cfd2ece.avif?t=1764149792 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A <strong>2D point-and-click adventure</strong> inspired by the great classics of the '90s, like <i><strong>Monkey Island, Day of the Tentacle, and Sam &amp; Max: Hit the Road.</strong></i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story full of humor and unexpected twists.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An exotic setting in a mysterious archipelago.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over <strong>50 fully illustrated</strong> and <strong>hand-colored locations</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Clever puzzles and hilarious conversations</strong> with a wide cast of characters.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Available on <strong>Mac OS / Steam / Linux.</strong>  </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras/f4252bd3ed41484ff5b9a214cb661971.poster.avif?t=1764149792\" width=800 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras/f4252bd3ed41484ff5b9a214cb661971.webm?t=1764149792\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321550/extras/f4252bd3ed41484ff5b9a214cb661971.mp4?t=1764149792\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
